            <h2>Primefinance Global Personal Insurance</h2>
            <p>NovaTrust Bank personal insurance is designed to give you and your family complete financial protection against the unexpected. We offer a wide range of cover options including life insurance, home insurance, health insurance and vehicle insurance, all under one roof. Each policy is fully customisable so you only pay for the cover you actually need, with no unnecessary add-ons or confusing terms and conditions.</p>
            <p>With NovaTrust Bank's online banking platform, managing your insurance has never been more convenient. You can access all your policy documents, make premium payments, update your personal details and submit claims directly through your secure online account at any time of the day or night. Our digital claims process is fast, paperless and transparent, so you always know exactly where your claim stands from submission to settlement.</p>
            <p>Choosing NovaTrust Bank for your personal insurance means choosing a provider that puts your wellbeing first. We offer competitive premiums, guaranteed renewals and a dedicated support team available Monday to Friday from 8:30am to 5:00pm to assist you with any questions or concerns. Whether you are taking out cover for the first time or switching from another provider, our insurance advisors are here to make the process as smooth and straightforward as possible.</p>


